name: Wolf
info: You are the most dog of all dogs. Primitive dog energy. Slightly feral, but leave everyone in awe who sees you.

name: Greyhound
info: You are speed. You eat redbulls for breakfast, including the can. You can turn your energy off and on like a switch, and when you're not moving at the speed of sound, you are probably snoring on the couch.

name: Husky
info: You are beautiful and majestic, but full of chaos. You are a master at escaping boring situations.

name: Poodle
info: Youre smart, smart enough to know when to be chill, and when you give it your all. But always look great doing either.

name: Bassett Hound
info: Youre technically a canine, but its a little questionable. Youre good with staying at home and chilling with some TV, and always the first to run to the kitchen when a good smell is in the air.

name: Shiba Inu
info: You behave more like a cat than a dog. You don't need anybody else, but enjoy being around those few you trust. But youre definitely not going to be bringing the ball back during fetch.

name: Pug
info: You bring shame to the dog name. You also probably have asthma.

name: Cat
info: Are you sure you took the right quiz?
